data.description: Meticulously maintained and newly renovated duplex is centrally located in the major metropolitan area of Fort Lauderdale.  One bedroom and one bathroom on each side. Three parking spaces plus room for a motorcycle or bicycles. Inside each of the units brings a cozy and welcoming ambiance. The kitchens may be compact, but they still allow you to prepare gourmet meals. Additionally, there are ample closet spaces available. Outside unit one is an ideal sitting area for meditation or to sip your morning coffee. The backyard is a lush sanctuary, with room for multiple seating areas and a has majestic trees which makes a perfect setting for outdoor dining and cherished moments. This duplex combines serenity with convenience. Take this opportunity to schedule your viewing today.
